{"title_page": "The Medium (video game)", "text_new": "{{Use dmy dates|date=May 2020}}\n{{Use British English|date=May 2020}}\n{{Infobox video game\n| title      = The Medium\n| image      = The medium game.jpg\n| developer  = [[Bloober Team]]\n| publisher  = \n| producer   = Jack Zieba<ref name=\"Romano-May2020\" />\n| designer   = Wojciech Piejko\n| programmer = \n| artist     = \n| writer     = Andrzej M\u0105drzak<ref name=\"Woolsey-May2020\" />\n| composer   = {{ubl|Arkadiusz Reikowski|[[Akira Yamaoka]]}}\n| engine     = \n| platforms  = {{ubl|[[Microsoft Windows]]|[[Xbox Series X]]}}\n| released   = {{ubl|{{Video game release|WW|Q4 2020}}}}\n| genre      = [[Psychological horror]]\n| modes      = [[Single-player]]\n}}\n'''''The Medium''''' is a [[psychological horror]] video game developed by [[Bloober Team]].\n\n==Gameplay==\n''The Medium'' is a [[psychological horror]] game played in [[Third-person view|third-person]] as Marianne, a [[Mediumship|medium]] who can travel into the spirit realm.<ref name=\"Takahashi-May2020\" /><ref name=\"Wales-May2020\" />\n\n==Development and release==\n''The Medium'' is developed by [[Bloober Team]].<ref name=\"Takahashi-May2020\" /> Bloober meant to enhance the immersion by changing the player's perspective from [[First-person (video games)|first-]] to third-person (contrary to their other releases) and taking advantage of [[Xbox Series X]]'s background streaming. Lead designer Wojciech Piejko said ''The Medium'' imparts the message that \"there is no universal truth\".<ref name=\"Wales-May2020\" /> The score is composed by Arkadiusz Reikowski and [[Akira Yamaoka]].<ref name=\"Takahashi-May2020\" /> Yamaoka worked on the ''[[Silent Hill]]'' franchise, which inspired the game.<ref name=\"Woolsey-May2020\" />\n\n''The Medium'' was originally announced for [[Xbox 360]], [[PlayStation 3]], and [[Wii U]] in 2012, but for want of better technology,<ref name=\"Wales-May2020\" /> reappeared in May 2020 as a [[Microsoft Windows]] and Xbox Series X title, scheduled to be released in the fourth quarter of 2020.<ref name=\"Takahashi-May2020\" />\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist|refs=\n\n<ref name=\"Takahashi-May2020\">{{cite web|last=Takahashi|first=Dean|date=7 May 2020|url=https://venturebeat.com/2020/05/07/the-medium-is-a-next-gen-psychological-horror-game-from-blair-witch-maker-bloober/|title=The Medium is a next-gen psychological horror game from Blair Witch maker Bloober|website=[[GamesBeat]]|archive-url=http://archive.today/2020.05.08-101054/https://venturebeat.com/2020/05/07/the-medium-is-a-next-gen-psychological-horror-game-from-blair-witch-maker-bloober/|archive-date=8 May 2020|url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"Wales-May2020\">{{cite web|last=Wales|first=Matt|date=7 May 2020|url=https://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2020-05-07-layers-of-fear-dev-bloober-talks-its-xbox-series-x-survival-horror-throwback-the-medium|title=Layers of Fear dev Bloober talks its Xbox Series X survival horror throwback The Medium|website=[[Eurogamer]]|archive-url=http://archive.today/2020.05.08-110232/https://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2020-05-07-layers-of-fear-dev-bloober-talks-its-xbox-series-x-survival-horror-throwback-the-medium|archive-date=8 May 2020|url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"Woolsey-May2020\">{{cite web|last=Woolsey|first=Cameron|date=7 May 2020|url=https://www.pcinvasion.com/bloober-team-reveal-the-medium/|title=Bloober Team shows off its next spooky game, The Medium|website=PC Invasion|archive-url=http://archive.today/2020.05.08-112100/https://www.pcinvasion.com/bloober-team-reveal-the-medium/|archive-date=8 May 2020|url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"Romano-May2020\">{{cite web|last=Romano|first=Nick|date=7 May 2020|url=https://ew.com/gaming/xbox-series-x-games-revealed/|title=Xbox Series X game trailers revealed: Assassin's Creed, psychological horror, and more|website=[[Entertainment Weekly]]|archive-url=http://archive.today/2020.05.08-113533/https://ew.com/gaming/xbox-series-x-games-r